# Literary Lounge: An Online Bookstore

## Description
Literary Lounge is a dynamic online bookstore platform that offers a seamless shopping experience for book lovers. Built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Node.js, users can explore a vast collection of books, manage their cart, and complete purchases effortlessly.

## Features
- User-friendly interface for easy navigation
- Search functionality to find books quickly
- Shopping cart management for a smooth checkout experience
- User authentication to manage accounts (if applicable)
- Reviews and ratings system to help users make informed decisions

## Technologies Used
- **Front-end**: 
  - HTML5
  - CSS3
  - JavaScript
  - React.js
- **Back-end**: 
  - Node.js
  - Express.js (if used)
- **Database**: 
  - MongoDB / PostgreSQL (if applicable)
- **Other**: 
  - npm, Git, GitHub

